    <abstract>
      <t>Inband Flow Analyzer (IFA) records flow specific information from smart NIC and/or switches across the network. This document discusses the method to collect the data on a per hop basis across the network and perform localized analytics operations on it. This document also describes transport agnostic header definition for tunneled and non tunneled flows.</t>
